This profile represents the constraints applied to the Bundle resource by the Electronic Product Information (ePI) FHIR Implementation Guide.
This profile provides an example of how the Composition (ePI) profile can be specialized to represent a Product information Leaflet withi a specific jurisdiction

Clinical document used to represent the Electronic Product Information (ePI) data set. An Electronic Product Information (ePI) document is an authorised, statutory product information for medicines (i.e. summary of product characteristics, package leaflet and labelling) in a semi-structured format created using the common EU electronic standard.
This profile represents the constraints applied to the List resource by the Electronic Product Information (ePI) FHIR Implementation Guide.
